 <H1>Importance of Open Dynamic Systems</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Model existing dynamic systems
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>operating systems, OLE- and CORBA-based systems
<LI>usability, scalability, integration, distribution
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Growing number of systems require �continuous availability�
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>mission- and safety- critical systems
<LI>adapt to changing environment, reduce the cost/risk of shutdown and restart
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Commercial end-user applications
